      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it still looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! It\u2019s been kept in a climate-controlled garage and the interior is basically flawless. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for perfectly, this is the one. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
