      "description": "This vehicle is a breathtaking example of automotive preservation, presented in true showroom condition. The exterior boasts its original factory paint, enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating that creates a deep, liquid-like luster, entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather seats remain firm and free of any bolster wear, the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty liners since day one, and the dashboard remains pristine with no UV fading. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, operates with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by master technicians using OEM parts. The engine bay is meticulously detailed, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, reflecting a life spent in a climate-controlled garage. Included are all original keys, the complete owner\u2019s manual set, and a comprehensive folder of service records. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle.",
